  "text": "In summary, the studies described above have clearly shown that ivacaftor is associated with significant health improvements in patients with the Gly551Asp CFTR mutation, who account for 5 % of people with cystic fibrosis, and have highlighted the beneficial role of this drug as a targeted therapy [CITATION_1] .",
